Subject: [PATCH] ASoC: Intel: sof_sdw: reduce log level for not using internal dmic
Mime-version: 1.0
Content-type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-transfer-encoding: 8bit
Git-commit: 90a73807fd8a6c044cc971e53c2cc602f3841ef6
